## Run Locally

Clone the project.

```bash
  git clone https://github.com/Harshsutaria/qp-assessment.git
```

Go to the project directory

```bash
  cd qp-assessment
```

build docker image using

```bash
  docker build -t stock-microservice
```

Start the server

```bash
  docker run -p 4000:4000 stock-microservice
```
